This isn't for wL, and will not work for it unless you do heavy modifying. Make backups of any file modified before modifying to save yourself. I cannot be at fault if you lose any data or resets occur. This has been tested thoroughly. If you need an app to add the Serializable character files to a MySQL database, create one yourself. 

